<%- include('partials/header') %>
    <section class="container py-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary">FAQ</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">Frequently Asked Questions</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            What days can I rent a dumpster?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Dumpsters are available for delivery Mondays and Thursdays.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            When will my dumpster be delivered?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Dumpsters will be delivered anytime between 7:30 AM to 3:00 PM.
                            We cannot guarantee specific delivery times.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            How many times can I rent a dumpster?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Residents are limited to one (1) dumpster rental up to three (3) times per calendar year.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            I don't live in Draper, can I rent a dumpster?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            No, the dumpster rental program is restricted to addresses within Draper, Utah only.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            Can I rent a dumpster for a group?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Yes, neighborhood groups, HOAs, and volunteer groups located within Draper City are
                            limited to Monday delivery only and are limited to no more than four (4) dumpster rentals
                            at a time, up to two (2) times per calendar year.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            What sizes of dumpster do you offer?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            We offer two sizes of dumpster:
                        <ul>
                            <li>20-Yard - $120 rental fee (16' L x 6' H x 8' W, weight limit 6 tons)</li>
                            <li>30-Yard - $150 rental fee (22' L x 6' H x 8' W, weight limit 10 tons)</li>
                        </ul>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            What is your cancellation policy?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            We offer two sizes of dumpster:
                            Cancellations must be made at least five (5) days before the delivery date to get a refund.
                            All cancellations will be charged a $10 bookkeeping fee.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title text-primary">
                            What am I allowed to put in the dumpster?
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            The dumpster may be used for yard debris (tree limbs, shrubbery, grass clippings, etc.) as well
                            as building materials, household items, some appliances, furniture, etc. Items that are not
                            acceptable
                            in the dumpster are toxic, hazardous or flammable materials such as pesticides, herbicides,
                            solvents,
                            chemicals, paints, motor oil, gasoline, etc. Also, tires, batteries, freezers and refrigerators, and
                            metal or platic drums (unless the tops are cut off) may not be deposited in the dumpster. Please
                            call
                            385-468-3862 for hazardous wastes disposal. The responsible party signing for the dumpster will be
                            liable
                            for the illegal placement of these items or any spillage from overloading the dumpster.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>